data.description: Rare Find! Built In 2015, This Gorgeous 4 Bed, 3 Bath Home Has Everything You Need Nestled Into The Charming Fountain Avenue Neighborhood. Step Through The Front Door To Find An Eye Catching Open-concept Living, Dining & Kitchen Area With Breathtaking Custom Built Cabinetry, Stainless Appliances, Bar Area, And Beautiful Countertops And Backsplash. The Dreamy Master Bath Includes A Tiled, Rainfall Shower, Double Vanity And Walk-in Closet. Upstairs You Will Find 2 More Bedrooms And Full Bath Along With A Lofted Living Area. Walk Through The Backyard Perfect For Entertaining To Find The 2-car Detached Garage, Temperature Controlled With An Upstairs Bonus Space.
